onal Award for Women shall be invited from the following:-State Govt., Union Territory Administrations, Concerned Central Ministries / Departments.Non-Governmental Organizations (NGOs), Universities / Institutions, Private and Public Sector Undertakings (PSUs).Selection Committee can also recommend any women individual or institution for the award with sufficient justificationWomen can also fill Self-nominations for the awards.WCD Ministry will constitute a Screening Committee to scrutinize and shortlist nominations on the basis of achievements of individuals / institutions. A Selection Committee will also be formed to select the awardees on the basis of recommendation of Screening committee.Eligibility Criteria for Nari Shakti Puraskar 2018-19National awards will inspire the individuals & institutions to follow the league of awardees:-Any individual or institution can fill the nominations for Nari Shakti Puraskar.For individual category, awardee must be above 25 years of age on last date on receipt of nomination.In case the applicant is an institution, then institutions should have worked in relevant field for at-least for at-least 5 years.Any applicant who had received this same award or Stree Shakti Puraskar earlier will not be eligible.This National Award 2018-19 may be awarded for outstanding work, preferably in exceptional circumstances to any individual / group /institutions / NGOs resulting in socio-economic empowerment of women. Also, this Highest Civilian Award could be given for encouraging women to participate in decision making roles, encouraging skill development in traditional & non-traditional sectors, providing basic amenities for rural women, promoting women in sectors such as science and technology, sports, art, culture, etc.Nari Shakti Puruskar 2018-19 shall be given to a State / UT in case the state has appreciably improved Child Sex Ratio (CSR).Normally, any individual or institution does not get this award posthumously. But if the death occurs after submitting the proposal, then such applications are accepted.Nari Shakti Puraskar shall be presented to the selected candidates at New Delhi. National Award will be confered on a special ceremony held on the occasion of International Women\u2019s Day on 8th March.References\u2014 For more details, check the complete guidelines at :- http://www.wcd.nic.in/sites/default/files/Guidelines%20Approved%20by%20the%20Minister.pdf  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}